    public class Comment
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICacheable<Comment>, java.lang.Comparable<Comment>, java.io.Serializable
    Author:
    mcmorris Comment is an instance of any posted comment. Support for node navigation is provided by Thread. Implements ICacheable - Serialization and Load support from file. Comparable - Allows for sorting on Comments
